data.title: Wilhelms, 1993
data.text:
Description

The human history of the Moon exploration programs, from a geologist's point of view.

This is not just "a moonbook"

It is much more... first of all it's a guide for those who want to search or want to know lots of names of selenologists and geologists, while simultaneously browsing through the pages of Wikipedia! - DannyCaes Dec 17, 2016

This book is the Double Helix of the Moon (Charles A. Wood).

Additional Information

This great book is now online.

Don E. Wilhelms on Wikipedia: Donald Wilhelms - Don Edward Wilhelms, and on The Moon (Wikispaces): Don E. Wilhelms.
